name: SURPRISE ME
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - There’s a surprise coming.
 
You can’t know what it is otherwise it wouldn’t be a surprise !  Think back over your life, are there any ‘out of the blue’ moments that shifted things for you or maybe even changed the whole course of
your life? Falling in love? Landing a new job? Meeting an old friend by chance? 

Human beings love surprises. Imagine a life where you knew exactly what was going to happen everyday until the day you die. How dreary, how boring. Open up to the surprises and be ready for this one because it's coming.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
